films.title: Barbie
films.description: In Barbieland, a matriarchal society, Barbie and her fellow Barbies lead successful lives while their Ken counterparts focus on leisure activities. When Barbie experiences existential worries and physical changes, she embarks on a journey into the real world to find the child playing with her. Along the way, she is joined by Ken, and together they confront issues of identity, gender roles, and unrealistic beauty standards. With the help of newfound friends, they challenge the patriarchal system and bring positive change to Barbieland, promoting equality and self-discovery.

films.title: Transformers: Rise of the Beasts
films.description: The Maximals, an advanced race of Transformers with beast modes, are under attack by the planet-eating dark god Unicron. The Terrorcons, led by Scourge, seek to obtain the Transwarp Key, a powerful device capable of opening portals through space and time. As the Autobots team up with humans, they must prevent Unicron's arrival on Earth, while facing internal conflicts and a difficult choice between returning home and protecting their new home planet.

films.title: Creed 3
films.description: Adonis Creed, a retired boxer, faces a complex journey of redemption and forgiveness when his troubled childhood friend, Damian Anderson, resurfaces. As family bonds and old wounds collide, Adonis must confront his past to step back into the ring for an emotional "Battle of Los Angeles" that will change his life forever.

films.title: Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny
films.description: Indiana Jones embarks on a thrilling adventure involving the Antikythera mechanism, time fissures, and a quest to stop an evil plot that could alter history. With old friends and new allies, he ventures through different eras, fighting villains and discovering ancient secrets.

films.title: John Wick: Chapter 4
films.description: John Wick seeks vengeance against the High Table, facing deadly assassins and a challenging duel to free himself from obligations. With friends and allies, he fights his way through a relentless pursuit of revenge.

films.title: Ant-Man and the Wasp: Quantumania
films.description: Scott Lang and Hope van Dyne venture into the Quantum Realm, encountering a powerful exiled traveler named Kang, who threatens multiple timelines.

films.title: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3
films.description: The Guardians face personal and cosmic challenges as they discover the truth about Star-Lord's heritage and the dark history of the Spartax. They encounter old enemies, make new allies, and must find a way to prevent the resurrection of Thanos.

films.title: Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore
films.description: In this next installment of the Fantastic Beasts series, Newt Scamander teams up with Albus Dumbledore to face an escaped dark wizard who is on a quest to destroy the peace between magical and non-magical worlds.

films.title: Avatar 2
films.description: The sequel to the 2009 film Avatar continues the epic journey of Jake Sully and Neytiri as they explore new areas of Pandora, face new threats, and fight for the future of the Na'vi and their planet.

films.title: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness
films.description: Doctor Strange faces dark and unexpected threats from different dimensions and must unleash the full potential of the mystic arts to save the world and protect reality itself.

films.title: The Flash
films.description: Barry Allen, aka The Flash, discovers new abilities and time-traveling possibilities. As he navigates through alternate timelines, he faces a devastating event that could impact the entire multiverse.

films.title: Jurassic World: Dominion
films.description: The dinosaurs now roam freely in the world, but when an unforeseen threat emerges, Owen Grady and Claire Dearing must come up with a plan to save both the dinosaurs and humanity from extinction.

films.title: Mortal Kombat 2
films.description: In the sequel to Mortal Kombat, the champions of Earthrealm must regroup and prepare for a new battle against the forces of Outworld, while a new threat emerges from the depths of the Netherrealm.

films.title: Sherlock Holmes 3
films.description: Sherlock Holmes and Dr. John Watson return for a new mystery that takes them to exotic locations and pits them against a nemesis from Sherlock's past, who seeks to unleash chaos on the world.

films.title: Black Panther: Wakanda Forever
films.description: Following the events of Avengers: Endgame, Wakanda faces new challenges and wonders who is worthy to take on the mantle of the Black Panther and protect the nation.

films.title: The Batman
films.description: In his second year as Batman, Bruce Wayne faces corruption in Gotham City and battles a mysterious and powerful foe, The Riddler, who challenges him in intellectual and physical ways.

films.title: Shazam! Fury of the Gods
films.description: Shazam faces new enemies, the deadly daughters of Atlas, who seek to unleash their godly wrath upon the world. With the help of his foster family, Shazam must harness his powers and unlock new abilities to save humanity.

films.title: Fast & Furious X
films.description: The tenth installment in the Fast & Furious franchise brings more high-speed action and heists as Dom Toretto and his crew face their toughest adversary yet.

films.title: The Northman
films.description: Amidst the rugged beauty of 10th-century Iceland, a Viking prince seeks revenge for his father's death, plunging him into an epic quest that will bring honor to his family.

films.title: The Lost City
films.description: A reclusive romance novelist and her cover model embark on an adventure to find her kidnapped hero, leading them into a jungle full of danger, treasure, and unexpected romance.

films.title: Halloween Ends
films.description: The final chapter in the Halloween trilogy follows the epic confrontation between Michael Myers and Laurie Strode, culminating in a deadly showdown.

films.title: Sonic the Hedgehog 2
films.description: Sonic and his new friend Tails team up to protect the Chaos Emeralds from the villainous Dr. Robotnik and his creation, Metal Sonic, in this action-packed adventure.

films.title: The Color Purple
films.description: An adaptation of Alice Walker's Pulitzer Prize-winning novel, the film follows the life of Celie Harris and her journey to find love, self-worth, and liberation despite facing oppression and adversity.

films.title: The Super Mario Bros.
films.description: An animated adventure follows the iconic Mario brothers as they set out to rescue Princess Peach from the clutches of the villainous Bowser and save the Mushroom Kingdom.

films.title: Black Adam
films.description: Teth-Adam, a former slave given the powers of six Egyptian gods, becomes the anti-hero Black Adam and seeks vengeance on those who wronged him. He must confront a new threat and find his place in the modern world.

films.title: Spider-Man: Across the Spider-verse
films.director: Joaquim Dos Santos, Justin K. Thompson, Kemp Powers
films.description: After reuniting with Gwen Stacy, Brooklyn's full-time, friendly neighborhood Spider-Man is catapulted across the Multiverse, where he encounters a team of Spider-People charged with protecting its very existence. However, when the heroes clash on how to handle a new threat, Miles finds himself pitted against the other Spiders. He must soon redefine what it means to be a hero so he can save the people he loves most.

films.title: Borat: Cultural Learnings of America for Make Benefit Glorious Nation of Kazakhstan
films.description: Borat Sagdiyev, a bumbling and clueless Kazakh journalist, travels to the United States to produce a documentary about American society and culture. Along the way, he interacts with real people who have no idea that he is a fictional character, leading to hilarious and often controversial situations. As Borat's encounters unfold, the film satirizes cultural differences, stereotypes, and societal norms.

films.title: Harold
films.description: Directed by Chett
